

Your Automated Cloud (YAC) - Service

Available comands include:

  yac service (-h | primer)

-h provides api help
primer will display this page or the naming/vpc primer page

Say your buddy developed bitchin/redis and you want to contribute some improvements.

Steps from nothing to ka-ching include:

1) Clone bitchin/redis service:
>> yac service --clone=bitchin/redis:1.3

2) Make and test updates to service template

3) Register your updates
>> yac service --register <path to template>